summary:
so Speak Now was the first song i ever learned on guitar.
and Taylor Swift is the reason why I ever even picked up a guitar and...
body:
so Speak Now was the first song i ever learned on guitar.

and Taylor Swift is the reason why I ever even picked up a guitar and learned to play.

It has added so much happiness to my life, just like she has.

and so, Taylor singing Speak Now in 2018, while doing better than she ever was, means more than she might ever know ♡
